    <subfield code="y">00000 Magnetic monopole (red arrows) created by a charge $e$ in magnetoelectric media with the coupling $\alpha\v E\cdot\v B$.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="856" ind1="4" ind2=" ">
